S.FORM: Australian Antarctic Territory kmal mha Astralian ga, maki' squ rhzyal na 南極洲 ga, kya qu rhzyal nha' ma. kinkhmay na squliq nya' ga, ini' tehuk 1000, cinrhzyal nya' ga, 5,896,500 km2. spzyang kinhopa' na rhzyal ga, TongFangCan( biqan nya' Russia ru kblayun nha' Kenkyu), kingwagiq nya' ga, 4030m.
